scene.message:
Brown: Kozai was a real{nl}
beauty, huh...{waitkey}Hey Mark, why don't you go{nl}
get kidnapped in her place.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Chisato Kozai...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Missing here too, is she.{waitkey}The god of fate must truly{nl}
despise her.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Did Kozai really like{nl}
Naito, I wonder?{waitkey}{clearbox}I mean, no matter how you{nl}
look at it, he's not her{nl}
type at all.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Sonomura's painting{nl}
won another prize in a{nl}
competition. I'm proud, even{nl}
as an outsider.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Kozai, by contrast,{nl}
never won a prize{waitkey}and got taken away by that{nl}
girl in black. She really has{nl}
rotten luck.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: You haven't heard?{nl}
Kozai was carried off by a{nl}
girl in black.{waitkey}I can't bear to watch how{nl}
sorry I feel for Naito.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Maki was close with{nl}
Kozai, so she must be worried{nl}
sick.{waitkey}{ret}
